HIRING ☀️

As a UofTrees’ media committee member, you will have a passion for sustainability and create promotional material for our account. 

Under the guidance of the Director of Marketing and the Club Secretary , you will submit what you have created in a timely manner based on the set schedule. 

Add experience to your resume and be ellgible for CCR credit! 🌲 

This is an inclusive safe space for you to get creative 🔧

Complete the application form linked in our bio by Sept. 17th and candidates will be contacted via school email. 

Can’t wait to meet you all!

Catch us at @uc.huttonhouse ‘s Sustainability Club Fair! 
Come say hi, learn more about our club and about our other upcoming events! 🫶🏻 
We don’t bite, so stop by and we’re so excited to meet all of you!!❤️🙂‍↕️
